<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">7. Final Checklist for Rigor</h2>
<ul class="contains-task-list">
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Every major claim has at least one citation</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Key terms are formally defined before use</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Mathematical claims include proofs or proof sketches</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Empirical claims cite data sources</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Alternative explanations are considered and addressed</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Limitations of the proposal are acknowledged</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Each section connects explicitly to the central thesis</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Bibliography includes primary sources, not just secondary discussions</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Technical terms are used precisely and consistently</li>
<li class="task-list-item"><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Counterarguments are steelmanned before rebuttal</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
