</span></span><span><span>where </span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">$H(A </span><span class="token equation equation-command" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">\mid</span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);"> I) </span><span class="token equation equation-command" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">\approx</span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);"> </span><span class="token equation equation-command" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">\log</span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);"> |</span><span class="token equation equation-command" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">\mathcal</span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">{A}|$</span><span>.
