</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">\begin</span><span class="token" style="color: rgb(171, 178, 191);">{</span><span class="token" style="color: rgb(198, 120, 221);">remark</span><span class="token" style="color: rgb(171, 178, 191);">}</span><span>
</span></span><span><span>The exact value of </span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">$</span><span class="token equation equation-command" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">\delta</span><span class="token equation" style="color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">_c$</span><span> depends on the entropy rate of agent behavior, 
